{
  "stem": "5103.1",
  "chunk_idx": 4,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 7.1,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But because he had had this underground movement happening to him in Bergen op Zoom, he decided that it was important that he do something as well in Amsterdam.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And there were a lot of people that needed homes to go through before they found a home to stay for hiding.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "So this gentleman-- I don't know his name-- got in touch with him.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "I remember one evening there was a meeting, and my father said, you know, you go to bed.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And you know-- and there was a meeting.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And afterwards I heard, why are these people coming here in the nighttime and why are they sleeping?",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And it was mainly-- it was men and women, but it was only overnight.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "They used to come, then they used-- that was called like a, a through address.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Like, my father gave them that as a kind of a-- they escaped from wherever they had to gone from, and then he gave them a bed and a breakfast, whatever, or something.",
      "word_count": 33
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And, and then, in the morning, before I was awake, they had disappeared, gone.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "So that was his work that he was doing, and it was very dangerous.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And, you know, he still thought, I think, that he would help by doing those sort of things, and we would never be caught.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "I mean, it was impossible.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "Anybody like us would be caught, you know.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "But it looked very bad, because the raids were going on, and everywhere there was problem taking place.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And then one day, he said, look, it's getting bad.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "His mother was picked up.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "His two sisters were picked up.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And they were sent away.",
      "word_count": 5
    }
  ],
